OPTIONS


                                                              *g:FerretDispatch*
|g:FerretDispatch|                                          boolean (default: 1)

Controls whether to use vim-dispatch (and specifically, |:Make|) to run |:Ack|
searches asynchronously, when available. To prevent vim-dispatch from being
used, set to 0:
>
    let g:FerretDispatch=0
<
